// `ENS.sol` interface, originally authored by Nick Johnson and the ENS Labs
// team, licensed under MIT.
//   Source : https://github.com/ensdomains/ens-contracts
//   File   : contracts/registry/ENS.sol
//   © 2018 Nick Johnson / ENS Labs
